      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride without the brand-new price tag. Come check it out!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
