    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving inline-6 utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a precise valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-compression internals operate at peak efficiency. While the aesthetic shows minor road wear consistent with active use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine and clean interior. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
