    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper and a small, pea-sized ding on the rear passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. The interior is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery is free of rips or stains, showing only light creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles, with the most recent maintenance including a brake pad replacement and a cabin air filter swap. The tires have approximately 65% tread remaining, ensuring a safe ride for many miles to come. This car has been kept in a smoke-free environment and comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys. It is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
